            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<h1>self-PU</h1>\n<p>文章提出了一种新颖的PUL问题框架。先前的PUL方法集中精力于损失敏感上面，直接将未标记样本作为负样本进行损失优化，然后对于未标记样本中各个样本赋予不同权重进行学习。问题也很明显</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"http://www.void2024.top/posts/Self-PU_Self Boosted and Calibrated Positive-Unlabeled Training\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.void2024.top/posts/Self-PU_Self Boosted and Calibrated Positive-Unlabeled Training</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "http://www.void2024.top/posts/Self-PU_Self Boosted and Calibrated Positive-Unlabeled Training",
            "title": "Paper reading--《Self-PU Self Boosted and Calibrated Positive-Unlabeled Training》",
            "image": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xjtu-wjz/void2004/main/pics_for_post/frena.webp",
            "date_modified": "2024-09-09T00:00:00.000Z",
            "date_published": "2024-09-09T00:00:00.000Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "void",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
