            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<h1>OOD简介</h1>\n<p>OOD（out of distribution detection）是异常检测（Anomaly Detection）领域的一个重要分支，通俗来讲OOD检测的任务就是**识别出分布与模型</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"http://www.void2024.top/posts/OOD-intro\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.void2024.top/posts/OOD-intro</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "http://www.void2024.top/posts/OOD-intro",
            "title": "Paper reading--《OOD-intro》",
            "image": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xjtu-wjz/void2004/main/pics/121043535_p0.1aoxfetb9a.webp",
            "date_modified": "2023-09-22T00:00:00.000Z",
            "date_published": "2024-09-07T00:00:00.000Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "void",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<h1>能量分数概述</h1>\n<p>首先什么是能量分数方法介绍：</p>\n<p>一个模型区分OOD和ID数据的主要依据是它们的能量分数，这个就是energy-based方法。</p>\n<p>大致流程是这样：</p>\n<p>![alt text](..</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"http://www.void2024.top/posts/Energy-based Out-of-distribution Detection\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.void2024.top/posts/Energy-based Out-of-distribution Detection</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "http://www.void2024.top/posts/Energy-based Out-of-distribution Detection",
            "title": "Paper reading--《Energy-based Out-of-distribution Detection》",
            "image": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xjtu-wjz/void2004/main/pics_for_post/liuhua.webp",
            "date_modified": "2023-10-10T00:00:00.000Z",
            "date_published": "2023-10-10T00:00:00.000Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "void",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<p>平稳的一周，一边推进论文一边过日子，中间放了个中秋的假，好玩的事其实也不少，当然糟心的事也有。</p>\n<h1>钓鱼</h1>\n<p>跟罗神他们一起六个人跑去钓鱼，着实二十岁的年纪，三十岁的身体，四十岁的爱好了。深刻感受到钓</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"http://www.void2024.top/posts/周记week4 (9.16~9.22)\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.void2024.top/posts/周记week4 (9.16~9.22)</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "http://www.void2024.top/posts/周记week4 (9.16~9.22)",
            "title": "周记 week4 (9.16~9.22)",
            "image": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xjtu-wjz/void2004/refs/heads/main/pics_for_post/ee19160f4316289d26edeb98fab655e.webp",
