            "content_html": "<p>论文通篇简述了PU-learning几个经典的问题，并且详细介绍了PUL到底是什么。</p>\n<h1>PU-learning与传统半监督学习</h1>\n<p>PU-learning是传统半监督学习的变种，与传统半监督学习</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"http://www.void2024.top/posts/Learning From Positive and Unlabeled Data-A Survey\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.void2024.top/posts/Learning From Positive and Unlabeled Data-A Survey</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
